==人口==

===現在===

{| class="wikitable" style="float:right; margin-left:2em; width:40%; font-size:85%;" cellspacing="3"
!colspan="4"|'''對比數據'''<ref name="Edinburghpop1">{{cite web |url=http://download.edinburgh.gov.uk/Census_2001_City_Comparisons/CCTable1Population.pdf |title=Edinburgh Comparisons – Population and Age Structure |accessdate=2009-01-31 |publisher=City of Edinburgh Council |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090205201927/http://download.edinburgh.gov.uk/Census_2001_City_Comparisons/CCTable1Population.pdf |archivedate=2009年2月5日 }}</ref><ref name="Edinburghpop2">{{cite web |url=http://www.scrol.gov.uk/scrol/browser/profile.jsp?profile=Population&mainArea=edinburgh&mainLevel=Locality |title=Comparative Population Profile – Edinburgh Locality |accessdate=2009-01-31 |publisher=Scotland's Census Results Online (SCROL) |archive-date=2012-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204075258/https://www.scrol.gov.uk/scrol/browser/profile.jsp?profile=Population&mainArea=edinburgh&mainLevel=Locality |dead-url=no }}</ref>
|-
|'''[[2011年英國人口普查|2011年英國人口普查]]'''||'''愛丁堡'''||'''蘇格蘭'''
|-
|總人口||476,626||5,295,000
|-
|2001–2011年間人口增長||6.2%||5.0%
